-- Mitsubishi Heavy May Buy 3% Stake in Areva for $537 Million, Yomiuri Says
-- Tak Kumakura
-- 2010-04-27T22:02:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-27/mitsubishi-heavy-may-buy-3-stake-in-areva-for-537-million-yomiuri-says.html

          
          
             Mitsubishi Heavy Industries Ltd.
may buy a 3 percent stake in French nuclear power company Aveva
SA for about 50 billion yen ($537 million), the Yomiuri
newspaper reported, without saying where it obtained the
information.  
 The two companies, which already operate a joint venture,
may strengthen alliance, the report said.   
          
          


  


        